title: THE V16 PROJECT  from SACD in WMA Pro multichannel 96Khz 24bit
description: THE V16 PROJECT from SACD in WMA Pro multichannel 96Khz 24bit. An electro-acoustic ensemble. The music is based on 3 vehicles:spontaneous composition, pre-composed pieces, and sonic adventure. It must be said that this music is unusual.It features slide guitar, electric guitar and drums (lots) and odd sound effects this is not for the faint hearted so you have been warned. but if you want to try something a little different, then give this a try..it&#039;s in multichannel too!
